OL,3,CEngland fans in Dallas to cope with
OL,4,C35C heat and nearby tropical storms
OL,6,FWhen England fans descend on Dallas to
OL,7,Fwatch their team play its opening
OL,8,FWorld Cup game against Croatia on
OL,9,FWednesday, it's going to be hot and
OL,10,Fhumid.
OL,12,FFor them, it will feel like 100F -
OL,13,Fthat's 38C - and if that's not bad
OL,14,Fenough, there is a tropical storm on
OL,15,Fthe way too.
OL,17,FHere is the outlook for tonight's
OL,18,Fmatch.
OL,20,FWhat is the forecast?
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/5
