OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781729269
OL,3,CEngland fans in Dallas to cope with
OL,4,C35C heat and nearby tropical storms
OL,6,FWith temperatures of 34-35C in the
OL,7,Fpeak daytime heat, Dallas is set to be
OL,8,Fincreasingly hot and humid through the
OL,9,Fmiddle of the week.
OL,11,FBut it's likely to feel even hotter
OL,12,Fwith the high humidity and direct sun.
OL,14,FAmerican meteorologists have described
OL,15,Ftoday's weather as having a "triple-
OL,16,Fdigit heat index", meaning the air
OL,17,Fwill feel like 100F (38C) due to the
OL,18,Fcombination of high temperatures and
OL,19,Fhigh humidity.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
