OL,3,CEngland fans in Dallas to cope with
OL,4,C35C heat and nearby tropical storms
OL,6,FThis prevents sweat from evaporating,
OL,7,Fmaking it difficult for the body to
OL,8,Fcool itself.
OL,10,FEngland will play Croatia at 4pm Texan
OL,11,Ftime (9pm UK time).
OL,13,FThis is around the peak of the daytime
OL,14,Fheat so the retractable roof of the
OL,15,FAT&T Stadium will be closed, meaning
OL,16,Fthat conditions will be more
OL,17,Fcomfortable for both players and
OL,18,F80,000 spectators.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/5
