OL,3,CEngland fans in Dallas to cope with
OL,4,C35C heat and nearby tropical storms
OL,6,FThe Texas stadium is one of the
OL,7,Fbiggest in the NFL - and the soaring,
OL,8,Fdoomed roof is one of the biggest in
OL,9,Fthe world.
OL,11,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,12,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,13,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,14,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,16,FIs there a storm nearby?
OL,18,FThe National Hurricane Centre flagged
OL,19,Fthat a potential tropical storm in
OL,20,FGulf Of Mexico skimming the Texas
OL,21,Fcoastline.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/5
