PN,31405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F314A1781729269
OL,3,CEngland fans in Dallas to cope with
OL,4,C35C heat and nearby tropical storms
OL,6,FIt could be the first named storm of
OL,7,Fthe 2026 Atlantic Tropical Season.
OL,9,FWhile the storm is unlikely to hit
OL,10,FDallas, it is very close to Houston,
OL,11,Fwhere Portugal is due to play the DC
OL,12,FCongo at midday Texas time (6pm UK
OL,13,Ftime).
OL,15,FThere is heavy rain forecast nearby
OL,16,Fplus late thunderstorms expected
OL,17,Fthrough the late morning and a flood
OL,18,Fwatch is in place.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/5
